This product is an independent, clean-room Kotlin reimplementation of the
Espressif serial bootloader protocol. Protocol behavior was studied from:

  - esp-serial-flasher  (Espressif, Apache-2.0)
  - esptool-js          (Espressif, Apache-2.0)
  - esptool             (Espressif, GPL-2.0) — referenced for protocol details

The bundled flasher-stub blobs under core/src/main/resources/stubs/ originate
from Espressif's flasher stub as redistributed by esptool-js (Apache-2.0).
"ESP32", "ESP8266" and related marks are trademarks of Espressif Systems.
